            "faq_1_answer": "<p>Hyaluronic Acid is a powerful humectant that can hold up to 1000 times its weight in water. It helps to deeply hydrate the skin, plump fine lines, and maintain skin elasticity. This ingredient is suitable for all skin types and works well with other active ingredients.</p>",
