            "faq_2_question": "How does Niacinamide help with skin concerns?",
            "faq_2_answer": "<p>Niacinamide (Vitamin B3) is a versatile ingredient that helps regulate oil production, minimize the appearance of pores, improve skin texture, and reduce redness. It's gentle enough for sensitive skin and can be used morning and evening. Niacinamide also helps strengthen the skin barrier and provides antioxidant protection.</p>",
